[package]
name = "device"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = [ "The Servo Project Developers",]

[features]
bluetooth = [ "blurz", "blurdroid", "blurmac",]
bluetooth-test = [ "blurmock",]

[dependencies.blurmock]
version = "0.1.2"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"linux\")".dependencies.blurz]
version = "0.3"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"android\")".dependencies.blurdroid]
version = "0.1.2"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.blurmac]
path = "blurmac"
optional = true

[package]
name = "fontsan"
version = "0.4.0"
authors = [ "The Servo Project Developers",]
description = "Sanitiser for untrusted font files"
build = "build.rs"
license = "BSD-3-Clause"

[dependencies]
libc = "0.2"
miniz-sys = "0.1.7"

[build-dependencies]
cmake = "0.1"

[package]
name = "immeta"
version = "0.4.1"
authors = [ "Vladimir Matveev <vladimir.matweev@gmail.com>",]
description = "An image metadata parsing library"
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/netvl/immeta"
documentation = "http://netvl.github.io/immeta/"
readme = "Readme.md"
keywords = [ "image", "metadata",]
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
byteorder = "1.4"
num-traits = "0.2"
arrayvec = "0.7"

[[test]]
name = "test"
path = "test/mod.rs"

[package]
name = "mio"
version = "0.6.22"
license = "MIT"
authors = [ "Carl Lerche <me@carllerche.com>",]
description = "Lightweight non-blocking IO"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/mio/0.6.22/mio/"
homepage = "https://github.com/tokio-rs/mio"
repository = "https://github.com/tokio-rs/mio"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "io", "async", "non-blocking",]
categories = [ "asynchronous",]
include = [ "Cargo.toml", "LICENSE", "README.md", "CHANGELOG.md", "src/**/*.rs",]

[features]
with-deprecated = []
default = [ "with-deprecated",]

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"
slab = "0.4.0"
net2 = "0.2.29"
iovec = "0.1.1"
cfg-if = "0.1.9"

[dev-dependencies]
tempdir = "0.3.4"
bytes = "0.4.0"

[dev-dependencies.env_logger]
version = "0.4.0"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(target_os = \"fuchsia\")".dependencies]
fuchsia-zircon = "0.3.2"
fuchsia-zircon-sys = "0.3.2"

[target."cfg(unix)".dependencies]
libc = "0.2.54"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies]
miow = "0.3"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.winapi]
version = "0.3"
features = [ "std", "ioapiset", "winbase", "winerror",]

[[example]]
name = "minimal"

[[example]]
name = "eval"

[[test]]
name = "callback"

[[test]]
name = "capture_stack"

[[test]]
name = "custom_auto_rooter"

[[test]]
name = "custom_auto_rooter_macro"

[[test]]
name = "enumerate"

[[test]]
name = "evaluate"

[[test]]
name = "offthread"

[[test]]
name = "panic"

[[test]]
name = "property_descriptor"

[[test]]
name = "rooting"

[[test]]
name = "runtime"

[[test]]
name = "runtime_no_outlive"

[[test]]
name = "typedarray"

[[test]]
name = "typedarray_panic"

[[test]]
name = "stack_limit"

[[test]]
name = "vec_conversion"

[package]
name = "mozjs"
description = "Rust bindings to the Mozilla SpiderMonkey JavaScript engine."
repository = "https://github.com/servo/mozjs"
version = "0.14.1"
authors = [ "The Servo Project Developers",]
build = "build.rs"
license = "MPL-2.0"

[build-dependencies]
cc = "1"

[lib]
doctest = false

[features]
debugmozjs = [ "mozjs_sys/debugmozjs",]
jitspew = [ "mozjs_sys/jitspew",]
profilemozjs = [ "mozjs_sys/profilemozjs",]
uwp = [ "mozjs_sys/uwp",]

[dependencies]
lazy_static = "1"
libc = "0.2"
log = "0.4"
num-traits = "0.2"

[dependencies.mozjs_sys]
path = "../mozjs"

[package]
name = "mozjs_sys"
description = "System crate for the Mozilla SpiderMonkey JavaScript engine."
repository = "https://github.com/servo/mozjs/"
version = "0.68.2"
authors = [ "Mozilla",]
links = "mozjs"
build = "build.rs"
license = "MPL-2.0"
exclude = [ "mozjs/js/src/tests/**", "mozjs/js/src/octane/**", "mozjs/js/src/jit-test/**", "mozjs/js/src/jsapi-tests/**", "mozjs/js/src/doc/**",]

[features]
debugmozjs = []
profilemozjs = []
uwp = []
jitspew = []

[lib]
name = "mozjs_sys"
doctest = false

[dependencies]
encoding_c = "0.9.6"
encoding_c_mem = "0.2.5"
libc = "0.2"
libz-sys = "1.0"

[build-dependencies]
cc = "1.0"
walkdir = "2"

[build-dependencies.bindgen]
version = "0.62"
default-features = false
features = [ "runtime", "which-rustfmt",]

[package]
name = "naga"
version = "0.2.0"
authors = [ "Dzmitry Malyshau <kvarkus@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
description = "Shader translation infrastructure"
homepage = "https://github.com/gfx-rs/naga"
repository = "https://github.com/gfx-rs/naga"
keywords = [ "shader", "SPIR-V",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1"
fxhash = "0.2"
log = "0.4"
num-traits = "0.2"
thiserror = "1.0"

[features]
default = []
glsl-in = [ "pomelo",]
glsl-validate = []
glsl-out = []
serialize = [ "serde",]
deserialize = [ "serde",]
spirv-in = [ "petgraph", "spirv",]
spirv-out = [ "spirv",]
wgsl-in = []

[dev-dependencies]
difference = "2.0"
env_logger = "0.6"
ron = "0.6"

[dependencies.spirv]
package = "spirv_headers"
version = "1.4.2"
optional = true

[dependencies.pomelo]
version = "0.1.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]
optional = true

[dependencies.petgraph]
version = "0.5"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[package]
name = "servo-media"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Manish Goregaokar <manishsmail@gmail.com>",]

[lib]
name = "servo_media"
path = "lib.rs"

[dependencies.servo-media-audio]
path = "../audio"

[dependencies.servo-media-player]
path = "../player"

[dependencies.servo-media-streams]
path = "../streams"

[dependencies.servo-media-traits]
path = "../traits"

[dependencies.servo-media-webrtc]
path = "../webrtc"

[package]
authors = [ "Fernando Jiménez Moreno <ferjmoreno@gmail.com>",]
license = "MPL-2.0"
name = "servo-media-audio"
version = "0.2.0"

[lib]
name = "servo_media_audio"
path = "lib.rs"

[dependencies]
boxfnonce = "0.1"
euclid = "0.22"
log = "0.4"
serde_derive = "1.0.66"
serde = "1.0.66"
smallvec = "1"
speexdsp-resampler = "0.1.0"
num-complex = "0.2.4"

[dependencies.servo_media_derive]
path = "../servo-media-derive"

[dependencies.servo-media-player]
path = "../player"

[dependencies.servo-media-traits]
path = "../traits"

[dependencies.servo-media-streams]
path = "../streams"

[dependencies.petgraph]
version = "0.4.12"
features = [ "stable_graph",]

[dependencies.byte-slice-cast]
version = "0.2"

[dependencies.num-traits]
version = "0.2"

[package]
name = "servo-media-dummy"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "The Servo Project Developers",]

[lib]
name = "servo_media_dummy"
path = "lib.rs"

[dependencies]
boxfnonce = "0.1.0"
ipc-channel = "0.16"

[dependencies.servo-media]
path = "../../servo-media"

[dependencies.servo-media-audio]
path = "../../audio"

[dependencies.servo-media-player]
path = "../../player"

[dependencies.servo-media-streams]
path = "../../streams"

[dependencies.servo-media-traits]
path = "../../traits"

[dependencies.servo-media-webrtc]
path = "../../webrtc"

[package]
name = "servo-media-gstreamer"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "The Servo Project Developers",]

[build-dependencies]
regex = "1.0"
zip = "0.3.1"
lazy_static = "1.0"

[lib]
name = "servo_media_gstreamer"
path = "lib.rs"

[dependencies]
boxfnonce = "0.1.0"
mime = "0.3.13"
log = "0.4"

[dependencies.byte-slice-cast]
version = "0.2"

[dependencies.glib]
version = "0.9"

[dependencies.glib-sys]
version = "0.9"

[dependencies.gstreamer-sys]
version = "0.8"
features = [ "v1_8",]

[dependencies.gstreamer]
version = "0.15"

[dependencies.gstreamer-app]
version = "0.15"

[dependencies.gstreamer-audio]
version = "0.15"

[dependencies.gstreamer-base]
version = "0.15"

[dependencies.gstreamer-player]
version = "0.15"

[dependencies.gstreamer-sdp]
version = "0.15"

[dependencies.gstreamer-webrtc]
version = "0.15"
features = [ "v1_16",]

[dependencies.gstreamer-video]
version = "0.15"

[dependencies.ipc-channel]
version = "0.16"

[dependencies.lazy_static]
version = "1.2.0"

[dependencies.servo-media]
path = "../../servo-media"

[dependencies.servo-media-audio]
path = "../../audio"

[dependencies.servo-media-player]
path = "../../player"

[dependencies.url]
version = "2.0"

[dependencies.servo-media-streams]
path = "../../streams"

[dependencies.servo-media-traits]
path = "../../traits"

[dependencies.servo-media-webrtc]
path = "../../webrtc"

[dependencies.servo-media-gstreamer-render]
path = "render"

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \"linux\", target_os = \"dragonfly\", target_os = \"freebsd\", target_os = \"netbsd\", target_os = \"openbsd\"))".dependencies.servo-media-gstreamer-render-unix]
path = "render-unix"
features = [ "gl-egl", "gl-x11",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"android\")".dependencies.servo-media-gstreamer-render-android]
path = "render-android"

[package]
name = "servo-media-gstreamer-render"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "The Servo Project Developers",]

[lib]
name = "servo_media_gstreamer_render"
path = "lib.rs"

[dependencies.gstreamer]
version = "0.15"

[dependencies.gstreamer-video]
version = "0.15"

[dependencies.servo-media-player]
path = "../../../player"

[package]
name = "servo-media-gstreamer-render-unix"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "The Servo Project Developers",]

[features]
gl-egl = [ "gstreamer-gl/egl",]
gl-x11 = [ "gstreamer-gl/x11",]
gl-wayland = [ "gstreamer-gl/wayland",]

[lib]
name = "servo_media_gstreamer_render_unix"
path = "lib.rs"

[dependencies.glib]
version = "0.9"

[dependencies.gstreamer]
version = "0.15"

[dependencies.gstreamer-gl]
version = "0.15"

[dependencies.gstreamer-video]
version = "0.15"

[dependencies.servo-media-player]
path = "../../../player"

[dependencies.servo-media-gstreamer-render]
path = "../render"

[package]
name = "servo-media-player"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Fernando Jiménez Moreno <ferjmoreno@gmail.com>", "Víctor Manuel Jáquez Leal <vjaquez@igalia.com>",]
license = "MPL-2.0"

[lib]
name = "servo_media_player"
path = "lib.rs"

[dependencies]
serde = "1.0.66"
serde_derive = "1.0.66"
ipc-channel = "0.16"

[dependencies.servo-media-streams]
path = "../streams"

[dependencies.servo-media-traits]
path = "../traits"

[package]
name = "servo-media-streams"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Manish Goregaokar <manishsmail@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"

[lib]
name = "servo_media_streams"
path = "lib.rs"

[dependencies]
lazy_static = "1.0"

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "0.8"
features = [ "v4",]

[package]
name = "servo-media-webrtc"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Josh Matthews <josh@joshmatthews.net>",]

[lib]
path = "lib.rs"

[dependencies]
boxfnonce = "0.1.0"
lazy_static = "1.0"
log = "0.4.6"

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "0.8"
features = [ "v4",]

[dependencies.servo-media-streams]
path = "../streams"

[package]
name = "servo_media_derive"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Fernando Jiménez Moreno <ferjmoreno@gmail.com>",]

[lib]
name = "servo_media_derive"
proc-macro = true
path = "lib.rs"

[dependencies]
syn = "1"
quote = "1"
proc-macro2 = "1"

[package]
name = "signpost"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Patrick Walton <pcwalton@mimiga.net>",]
description = "Rust interface to the OS native signpost debug facilities"
license = "MIT / Apache-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/pcwalton/signpost"

[dependencies]

[package]
name = "webxr"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = [ "The Servo Project Developers",]
edition = "2018"
homepage = "https://github.com/servo/webxr"
repository = "https://github.com/servo/webxr"
keywords = [ "webxr", "openvr", "oculus", "magicleap", "headset", "vr", "ar",]
license = "MPL-2.0"
description = "A safe Rust API that provides a way to interact with\nVirtual Reality and Augmented Reality devices and integration with\nvendor-specific APIs like OpenVR, Oculus, GoogleVR and Magic Leap. The\nAPI is inspired by the WebXR Device API (https://www.w3.org/TR/webxr/)\nbut adapted to Rust design patterns."
build = "build.rs"

[lib]
path = "lib.rs"

[features]
default = [ "x11",]
x11 = [ "surfman/sm-x11",]
angle = [ "surfman/sm-angle",]
egl = []
gles = []
glwindow = []
headless = []
ipc = [ "webxr-api/ipc", "serde",]
googlevr = [ "gvr-sys", "android_injected_glue", "gles",]
magicleap = [ "egl",]
openxr-api = [ "angle", "openxr", "winapi", "wio", "surfman/sm-angle-default",]
profile = [ "webxr-api/profile",]

[dependencies]
crossbeam-channel = "0.5"
euclid = "0.22"
log = "0.4.6"
sparkle = "0.1"
time = "0.1.42"

[build-dependencies]
gl_generator = "0.13"
bindgen = "0.62"

[dependencies.webxr-api]
path = "../webxr-api"

[dependencies.gvr-sys]
version = "0.7"
optional = true

[dependencies.openxr]
git = "https://github.com/servo/openxrs.git"
branch = "secondary-views-2"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.surfman]
version = "0.8"
features = [ "chains",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.winapi]
version = "0.3"
features = [ "dxgi", "d3d11", "winerror",]
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.wio]
version = "0.2"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"android\")".dependencies.android_injected_glue]
version = "0.2.2"
optional = true

[package]
name = "webxr-api"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = [ "The Servo Project Developers",]
edition = "2018"
homepage = "https://github.com/servo/webxr"
repository = "https://github.com/servo/webxr"
keywords = [ "webxr", "openvr", "oculus", "magicleap", "headset", "vr", "ar",]
license = "MPL-2.0"
description = "A safe Rust API that provides a way to interact with\nVirtual Reality and Augmented Reality devices and integration with\nvendor-specific APIs like OpenVR, Oculus, GoogleVR and Magic Leap. The\nAPI is inspired by the WebXR Device API (https://www.w3.org/TR/webxr/)\nbut adapted to Rust design patterns."

[lib]
path = "lib.rs"

[features]
ipc = [ "serde", "ipc-channel", "euclid/serde",]
profile = [ "time",]

[dependencies]
euclid = "0.22"
log = "0.4"

[dependencies.ipc-channel]
version = "0.16"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.time]
version = "0.1"
optional = true

[package]
name = "wgpu-core"
version = "0.6.0"
authors = [ "wgpu developers",]
edition = "2018"
description = "WebGPU core logic on gfx-hal"
homepage = "https://github.com/gfx-rs/wgpu"
repository = "https://github.com/gfx-rs/wgpu"
keywords = [ "graphics",]
license = "MPL-2.0"

[lib]

[features]
default = []
trace = [ "ron", "serde", "wgt/trace",]
replay = [ "serde", "wgt/replay",]
serial-pass = [ "serde", "wgt/serde", "arrayvec/serde",]

[dependencies]
arrayvec = "0.5"
bitflags = "1.0"
copyless = "0.1"
fxhash = "0.2"
gfx-backend-empty = "0.6"
parking_lot = "0.11"
smallvec = "1"
thiserror = "1"
gfx-descriptor = "0.2"
gfx-memory = "0.2"

[dev-dependencies]
loom = "0.3"

[build-dependencies]
cfg_aliases = "0.1"

[dependencies.hal]
package = "gfx-hal"
version = "0.6"

[dependencies.raw-window-handle]
version = "0.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.ron]
version = "0.6"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "serde_derive",]
optional = true

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1"
default-features = false
features = [ "std",]

[dependencies.naga]
version = "0.2"
git = "https://github.com/gfx-rs/naga"
rev = "b278e10ea7c144b2387585c4e81c1d86db8e2def"
features = [ "spirv-in", "spirv-out", "wgsl-in",]

[dependencies.wgt]
path = "../wgpu-types"
package = "wgpu-types"
version = "0.6"

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \"ios\", target_os = \"macos\"))".dependencies.gfx-backend-metal]
version = "0.6"

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \"ios\", target_os = \"macos\"))".dependencies.gfx-backend-vulkan]
version = "0.6"
optional = true

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(target_os = \"ios\"), not(target_os = \"macos\")))".dependencies.gfx-backend-vulkan]
version = "0.6.1"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.gfx-backend-dx12]
version = "0.6"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.gfx-backend-dx11]
version = "0.6"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.gfx-backend-vulkan]
version = "0.6"

[package]
name = "wgpu-types"
version = "0.6.0"
authors = [ "wgpu developers",]
edition = "2018"
description = "WebGPU types"
homepage = "https://github.com/gfx-rs/wgpu"
repository = "https://github.com/gfx-rs/wgpu"
keywords = [ "graphics",]
license = "MPL-2.0"

[lib]

[features]
trace = [ "serde",]
replay = [ "serde",]

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1.0"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "serde_derive",]
optional = true

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/servo/devices"]
git = "https://github.com/servo/devices"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "cb28c4725ffbfece99dab842d17d3e8c50774778"

[source."https://github.com/servo/fontsan"]
git = "https://github.com/servo/fontsan"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/fabricedesre/immeta"]
git = "https://github.com/fabricedesre/immeta"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/servo/mio"]
git = "https://github.com/servo/mio"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "servo-mio-0.6.22"

[source."https://github.com/servo/mozjs"]

replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/gfx-rs/naga"]
git = "https://github.com/gfx-rs/naga"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "b278e10ea7c144b2387585c4e81c1d86db8e2def"

[source."https://github.com/servo/media"]
git = "https://github.com/servo/media"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/pcwalton/signpost"]
git = "https://github.com/pcwalton/signpost"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

replace-with = "vendored-sources"

git = "https://github.com/gfx-rs/wgpu"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "e72724a6e393503c73f37e86aa9317a5c62e32b8"
